data.description: You will love this 3BR/2.5BA located in the Five Forks area in Simpsonville. Open great room and kitchen space, formal dining room, home office with french doors. Kitchen features granite counters, center island, modern appliances, plenty of cabinet space and closet pantry. Upstairs loft space is perfect for a home movie or gaming space. Spacious master suite with multiple walk in closets, private bath with double vanity, separate shower and garden tub. Patio and fenced back yard is perfect for entertaining friends and family for the upcoming summer season. Additional features include new roof installed in March 2023 with 50 year warranty, tankless hot water heater and radiant barrier in attic for energy efficiency.  Neighborhood features junior olympic pool with separate baby pool, cabana and playground. Call and schedule your tour today!
